          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Help Extend Auditory Relief (HEAR) Act of 2015 </b></p> <p> Amends title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to cover aural rehabilitation services, hearing aids as durable medical equipment, audiology rehabilitation services, and related hearing services.</p>]]></text>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2015-07-17T14:02:38Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
